headline: Stocks to Watch Wednesday Recap: Strategy, Boeing, Netflix, Paramount
summary: ↘️Boeing (BA): Shares turned lower in afternoon trading after President Trump criticized the defense industry and called for changes. Shares in the aerospace company had been higher earlier in the day after Alaska Air (ALK) said it would buy more than 100 new aircraft from Boeing.

headline: Newmont (NEM) Valuation Check After Strong Recent Share Price Momentum
summary: Why Newmont is on investors’ radar today Newmont (NEM) has drawn fresh attention after recent share moves, with the stock showing gains over the past week, month, and past 3 months that stand out against its longer term total return record. headline: Stocks to Watch Wednesday: Strategy, Applied Digital, Chevron
summary: ↗️ Strategy (MSTR): Shares of the bitcoin-accumulation company climbed 5% premarket after index provider MSCI said it won't exclude crypto treasury companies from its indexes. ↘️ Newmont (NEM), Freeport-McMoRan (FCX), Antofagasta (UK: ANTO): Global mining stocks came under pressure as a rally in precious and industrial metals stalled.
